Odell, Respondent, v. New York El. R. Co., Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November, 1889.) Appeal from trial term.

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Daly and Bookstaver, JJ.

Davies & Rapallo, for appellant. Sackett & Bennett, for respondent.

No opinion'. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
